<p>Fragment from the upper part of a <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs> front <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.90</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.335</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.16</measure> with upper part of <rs type="decoration">tabella ansata</rs> and a <rs type="decoration">putto</rs> in relief to left.
</p>
